    "body": "It seems that OS X only draws the shadow when the window is showed for the first time, so if you changed page's content after showing the window, the shadow will not be updated. The only solution is to show the window after you have created all DOM elements.\n\nI'm closing this as won't fix since it is a limitation of OS X.\n"
